  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_5_3152-3211",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3152-3211",
      "markText": "而杜林先生所设计的低温计或低温测量仪，既不是用来测量高温，也不是用来测量低温，而唯一地只是用来测量杜林先生的狂妄无知。",
      "totalCount": 675,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3152&rangeEnd=3211",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3152&rangeEnd=3211"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_6_405-437",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "405-437",
      "markText": "本书要出新版，是出乎我意料的。本书所批判的对象现在几乎已被遗忘了",
      "totalCount": 345,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=405&rangeEnd=437",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=405&rangeEnd=437"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_5_3018-3059",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3018-3059",
      "markText": "我深知自己在物理和化学方面的知识不够，可是我总相信，对于我的杜林先生我是很知底的。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3018&rangeEnd=3059",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3018&rangeEnd=3059"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_10_1229-1319",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1229-1319",
      "markText": "原则不是研究的出发点，而是它的最终结果；这些原则不是被应用于自然界和人类历史，而是从它们中抽象出来的；不是自然界和人类去适应原则，而是原则只有在符合自然界和历史的情况下才是正确的。",
      "totalCount": 324,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1229&rangeEnd=1319",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1229&rangeEnd=1319"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_9_4575-4582",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4575-4582",
      "markText": "中国人式的博学",
      "totalCount": 320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4575&rangeEnd=4582",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4575&rangeEnd=4582"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_8_1428-1475",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1428-1475",
      "markText": "18世纪伟大的思想家们，也同他们的一切先驱者一样，没有能够超出他们自己的时代使他们受到的限制。",
      "totalCount": 300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1428&rangeEnd=1475",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1428&rangeEnd=1475"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_16_8422-8484",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "8422-8484",
      "markText": "人们自觉地或不自觉地，归根到底总是从他们阶级地位所依据的实际关系中——从他们进行生产和交换的经济关系中，获得自己的伦理观念。",
      "totalCount": 300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=8422&rangeEnd=8484",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=8422&rangeEnd=8484"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_10_3391-3448",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "3391-3448",
      "markText": "世界体系的每一个思想映象，总是在客观上受到历史状况的限制，在主观上受到得出该思想映象的人的肉体状况和精神状况的限制",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3391&rangeEnd=3448",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3391&rangeEnd=3448"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_8_464-547",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "464-547",
      "markText": "现代社会主义，就其内容来说，首先是对现代社会中普遍存在的有财产者和无财产者之间、资产者和雇佣工人之间的阶级对立以及生产中普遍存在的无政府状态这两个方面进行考察的结果。",
      "totalCount": 260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=464&rangeEnd=547",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=464&rangeEnd=547"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_4_2754-2799",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2754-2799",
      "markText": "“暴力仅仅是手段，相反，经济利益才是目的。目的比用来达到目的的手段要具有大得多的‘基础性’",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2754&rangeEnd=2799",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2754&rangeEnd=2799"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_8_1148-1200",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1148-1200",
      "markText": "从今以后，迷信、非正义、特权和压迫，必将为永恒的真理、永恒的正义、基于自然的平等和不可剥夺的人权所取代。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1148&rangeEnd=1200",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1148&rangeEnd=1200"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_8_3423-3452",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3423-3452",
      "markText": "为了使社会主义变为科学，就必须首先把它置于现实的基础之上。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3423&rangeEnd=3452",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3423&rangeEnd=3452"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_16_2728-2810",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "2728-2810",
      "markText": "换句话说，思维的至上性是在一系列非常不至上地思维着的人中实现的；拥有无条件的真理权的认识是在一系列相对的谬误中实现的；二者都只有通过人类生活的无限延续才能完全实现。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2728&rangeEnd=2810",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2728&rangeEnd=2810"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_5_1873-1990",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1873-1990",
      "markText": "所谓科学自由(1)，就是人们可以著书立说来谈论自己从未学过的各种东西，而且标榜这是唯一的严格科学的方法。",
      "totalCount": 230,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1873&rangeEnd=1990",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1873&rangeEnd=1990"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_10_4535-4620",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "4535-4620",
      "markText": "但是，正像在其他一切思维领域中一样，从现实世界抽象出来的规律，在一定的发展阶段上就和现实世界脱离，并且作为某种独立的东西，作为世界必须遵循的外来的规律而同现实世界相对立。",
      "totalCount": 230,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4535&rangeEnd=4620",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4535&rangeEnd=4620"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025436_4_1743-1793",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1743-1793",
      "markText": "“自由不在于幻想中摆脱自然规律而独立，而在于认识这些规律，从而能够有计划地使自然规律为一定的目的服务",
      "totalCount": 228,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025436&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1743&rangeEnd=1793",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/19632000813ab706fg016c7a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1743&rangeEnd=1793"
